# Ignore Python backend files so Vercel doesn't try to build them.
# IMPORTANT: patterns must be anchored with / to match root-level dirs only.
# Without /, "src/" would also exclude frontend/src/ (the Next.js app).
*.py
pyproject.toml
requirements*.txt
/src/
/scripts/
/data/
/hipporag_index/
/runs/
/configs/
Dockerfile
fly.toml
README.md
